colophon_(төгсгөлийн_үг): @014A *, ,(ZHES CHOS RGYAL SKU LNGA DANG DAM CAN SKYES BU CHEN PO RNAMS LA GSER SKYEMS KYI MCHOD PA BYA TSUL 'DI NI RANG GI LHA GSOL SOGS KYI SKABS NYE BAR MKHO BAR BRTEN, ,SH'AKYA BTZUN SNYOMS LAS PA BSKAL BZANG BKRA SHIS RGYA MTSOS SBYAR BA'I YI GE PA NI RANG GI BU SLOB DPYOD YANGS DGE SLONG BSKAL BZANG YE SHES SO, ,'DIS KYANG SRUNG MA'I DBANG PO RNAMS DGYES PA BSKYED CING RANG GZHAN LA PHAN THOGS PAR GYUR CIG , ,,
